To export funds from a PBaaS chain to VRSCTEST, you can use the `sendcurrency` command. The format you'll want to use is:

```json
verus -chain=PBaaSChain sendcurrency "*" '[{"address":"your_address","amount":10, "convertto":"VRSCTEST","exportto":"VRSCTEST","via":"Bridge.PBaaSChain"}]'
```

This command will export the specified amount of funds from the PBaaS chain to VRSCTEST, using the Bridge on the PBaaS chain. Make sure to replace `"your_address"` with the actual address you want to send the funds to.
